This is a custom distribution of libRocket, version 1.2.2, with a XMake-based build
system.

The original README file of libRocket is at 'readme-librocket.md'.

Note: Unlike the official libRocket repository, this one doesn't include any example, nor
the Python bindings.


License
-------

libRocket's license is unchanged: this library is free software; you can redistribute
it and/or modify it under the terms of the MIT license. See the file 'readme-librocket.md'
for the details.


Submodules
----------

This distribution use XMake and FreeType as GIT submodules. To download them, do:

    $ git submodule init
    $ git submodule update


Compilation
-----------

It is recommended to compile the library in a separate folder. Here's how I do it:

    $ mkdir build
    $ cd build
    $ cmake ..
    $ make
